PLACEHOLDER – Replace with Apple WWDR G3 intermediate certificate (PEM format)

Steps:
  1. Download: https://www.apple.com/certificateauthority/AppleWWDRCAG3.cer
  2. Convert:  openssl x509 -inform DER -in AppleWWDRCAG3.cer -out wwdr.pem
  3. Replace this file with the resulting wwdr.pem

The file must start with:
  -----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
  ...
  -----END CERTIFICATE-----
